# NOTE: dist/ is intentionally committed.
# The package is consumed from a vendored Chassis checkout via file: dependency,
# which resolves `main: dist/index.js` / `types: dist/index.d.ts` at install time
# (no npm publish step runs). A committed dist/ keeps fresh clones usable without
# a build, and a chassis CI drift gate (codegen-ts-types job) fails the build if
# the committed output diverges from regenerating against the source schemas.
